graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]

    %% External Required Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|orchestration platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.19+]
    KubeRay -->|container runtime| Ray[Ray 2.9.0+<br/>Container Images]

    %% External Optional Dependencies
    KubeRay -.->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS fault tolerance| Redis[External Redis 6.0+]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|external access| Routes[OpenShift Route API]
    KubeRay -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Component-to-Component Interactions
    RayCluster[Ray Cluster] -->|coordination| K8s
    RayCluster -->|GCS persistence| Redis
    RayCluster -->|checkpoints & artifacts| S3[S3/Cloud Storage]
    RayCluster -->|runtime environments| Git[Git Repositories]
    RayCluster -->|container images| Registry[Container Registry]

    APIServer[KubeRay API Server<br/>Optional] -->|manages CRs| KubeRay
    APIServer -->|CRUD operations| K8s

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| KubeRay
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy workloads| KubeRay
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -.->|submit jobs| RayCluster

    %% User Interactions
    Users[Data Scientists /<br/>ML Engineers] -->|create CRs| KubeRay
    Users -->|submit jobs| RayCluster
    Users -->|REST/gRPC API| APIServer

    CI[CI/CD Systems] -->|automation| KubeRay
    CI -->|job submission| APIServer

    %% Monitoring & Observability
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| KubeRay
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| RayCluster

